This file documents the revision history for Mojolicious plugin Mojolicious::Plugin::Cms (Luzy).

0.011	2010-09-12 00:00:00
		- Error handling in admin edit action
		- Better CSV parsing in admin controller (code borrowed from Text::Tags::Parser)
		- Added save and create actions to admin
		- Changed Format to Converter
		- Updated /admin/edit.html.ep
		- Added Luzy::Plugin::Iso639 for language codes
		- Added Luzy namespace with "own" plugin support
		- fixed some internals and example
		- Remove support of the "empty" language.

0.01	2010-09-08 00:00:00		
		- Changed luzy.pl to show tags
		- Added all_tags and all_categories to store interface
		- Added Changes file
	